    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to check out my car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really wonderful shape! It drives super smoothly and has been well-loved, making it a perfect choice if you're looking for something solid and dependable without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve really enjoyed my time with it, and I\u2019m sure you will too. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
